This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning algorithms for solving verbal analogy questions and determining semantic relations in noun-modifier pairs. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Computation and Language (cs.CC).
